Each extension consists of an identifier and associated data. The structure is defined as follows:

    struct {
        ExtensionType extension_type;
        opaque extension_data<0..2^16-1>;
    } HandshakeExtension;

The Supported Versions extension has the following structure:


struct {
    ProtocolVersion versions<2..2^8-1>;
} SupportedVersions;


Where `versions` is a list of protocol versions supported by the client.

struct {
